la dilatation du temps dans un champ gravitationnel faible ouvre peut-être une voie expérimentale pour explorer cette interface mystérieuse entre le quantum et la géométrie de l'espace-temps.", "hash": "sha256:aa7f65fdbc78d9ba6d34335011c2cf4bd8c6e06f1f26333e99a5a04ba247003f"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "Le paradoxe du temps en mécanique quantique", "document_date": "15-03-2025", "keywords": ["#temps", "#physique_quantique", "#relativité", "#univers"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:45Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:27Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:5316a54035099f16088f7f576ec707fbc681ffab3db0ba4b07af0f398874f64f", "start": 0, "end": 1353, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "relativité générale d'Einstein", "span": [122, 152], "weight": null, "norm": "relativité générale d'einstein", "embedding_ref": "emb:0ef4b6cec5469d958d2efceaea6c11fe8f1b0d73fd0ce14561f54314f4fcd723"}, {"expression": "mécanique quantique", "span": [241, 260], "weight": null, "norm": "mécanique quantique", "embedding_ref": "emb:2d0c3ea6fffe1397faffa2384ced27d9214cfa740c7a9d0443e6fe12526a4814"}, {"expression": "théorie de la gravité quantique", "span": [431, 462], "weight": null, "norm": "théorie de la gravité quantique", "embedding_ref": "emb:048d7f580f3d57e12054990b13663db21fed86946eadd5bd0fcc9743fcdb94c9"}, {"expression": "gravitation quantique à boucles", "span": [495, 526], "weight": null, "norm": "gravitation quantique à boucles", "embedding_ref": "emb:aa2d128840db83199389e72c94800e2d2d4d85411c5fe8e2ba7aac97318cf482"}, {"expression": "théorie des cordes", "span": [608, 626], "weight": null, "norm": "théorie des cordes", "embedding_ref": "emb:1d693157983a0a3e9c648ac8e50c66790179d70fd4ecabfaf9e1fbaaf9e69ae7"}, {"expression": "horloge quantique d'Häfele et Keating", "span": [745, 782], "weight": null, "norm": "horloge quantique d'häfele et keating", "embedding_ref": "emb:964d6253f3229734ac9c474c45a2e3a143b2c6bd427c43a4544d7f4c59d43c6d"}, {"expression": "états superposés", "span": [802, 818], "weight": null, "norm": "états superposés", "embedding_ref": "emb:04343b269a30341987e5e0b51ac9fd29d557cf789bc545cb620ae69aaa093045"}, {"expression": "temps illusoire", "span": [956, 971], "weight": null, "norm": "temps illusoire", "embedding_ref": "emb:dfe84163d95f93cf805c9a47389c5c0130c37f8ac681d4d501a52ad13002a6e8"}, {"expression": "temps réel", "span": [1012, 1022], "weight": null, "norm": "temps réel", "embedding_ref": "emb:8e5e5a297f2d05f634f1cc203c0401b24b35f5cbe47c58d46f232a3507aa8b0c"}, {"expression": "expérience utilisant des interféromètres à atomes froids", "span": [1095, 1151], "weight": null, "norm": "expérience utilisant des interféromètres à atomes froids", "embedding_ref": "emb:5f391d7ef4a4383a3474fdcf46b6489f1b9ecb92879a17b7d22d5eedbd3c2dd7"}, {"expression": "dilatation du temps", "span": [1167, 1186], "weight": null, "norm": "dilatation du temps", "embedding_ref": "emb:8dc017d0ee97ebf2c71fd73609014071a18cc7c7b2e2375100ff0245ee23c486"}, {"expression": "champ gravitationnel faible", "span": [1195, 1222], "weight": null, "norm": "champ gravitationnel faible", "embedding_ref": "emb:8e6d00ef325036b188e12df187e40146596aff2e44ff58f56db4086d6b1466bc"}, {"expression": "interface mystérieuse", "span": [1282, 1303], "weight": null, "norm": "interface mystérieuse", "embedding_ref": "emb:deb372a32fb15d8510ee557572781fdb61697cf07a7b39c2162610539752133d"}, {"expression": "quantum et la géométrie de l'espace-temps", "span": [1313, 1354], "weight": null, "norm": "quantum et la géométrie de l'espace-temps", "embedding_ref": "emb:2ae90d28d4b538c5204d84f394301a0f4921554254dd2fe9cd8fb8597465c782"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 1, "source_expression": "mécanique quantique"}}}, {"id": 3631499317755308613, "score": 0.9999999403953552, "combined_score": 0.9999999403953552, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:27d79586c0b0e6827d27785f15ad492d5c0d6a9ae79deaf3f50bfe798f6d55ea", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:7bd2b643150bd39df0ee7399d929c8556c1eb565c684aad22e66f083606da6ea"}, "content": {"text": "L'informatique quantique représente une rupture majeure dans le paradigme du calcul. Contrairement aux bits classiques, les qubits peuvent exister dans un état de superposition, permettant de traiter une quantité exponentielle d'informations simultanément. Cette propriété ouvre la voie à des algorithmes révolutionnaires, comme celui de Shor, capable de factoriser de grands nombres en un temps polynomial, menaçant ainsi les systèmes cryptographiques actuels. Cependant, cette même puissance pourrait être canalisée pour créer des protocoles de chiffrement quantique inviolables, fondés sur les principes de la mécanique quantique. Le développement d'ordinateurs quantiques pratiques reste un défi de taille, impliquant la maîtrise de la décohérence et la mise à l'échelle des systèmes. Les recherches se poursuivent activement dans les laboratoires et les entreprises technologiques, laissant entrevoir une transformation profonde de nombreux secteurs.", "hash": "sha256:573320c237040c8a6c1643d8fbe07cf76a3ae4acbc9047a6e03839c153bd5cc2"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L'avenir de la cryptographie", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:26:37Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:26:24Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:8324e513d506d3e2f31fbb01567d78833043387eda8b3191a5fc03e8640827d0", "start": 0, "end": 955, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "informatique quantique", "span": [2, 24], "weight": null, "norm": "informatique quantique", "embedding_ref": "emb:6cab3d0f4daeb2b48b72e530f122c1c43f051487750d9cf80808630954e6684e"}, {"expression": "bits classiques", "span": [103, 118], "weight": null, "norm": "bits classiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:9e53e7c1e7df87af7c6221c40124b2969178d23f3a2dc06fe8ab160a250183ce"}, {"expression": "qubits", "span": [124, 130], "weight": null, "norm": "qubits", "embedding_ref": "emb:68597cad717e4dec57ad06b9be71c1371e5fd37c13d3f03ba442e36b8d95dac4"}, {"expression": "superposition", "span": [163, 176], "weight": null, "norm": "superposition", "embedding_ref": "emb:516c9965adc6a5b9fea33c747c8be3b863f09215ff1031a3506303dfe8c02cca"}, {"expression": "algorithmes révolutionnaires", "span": [293, 321], "weight": null, "norm": "algorithmes révolutionnaires", "embedding_ref": "emb:46f69ca6828850e7f56f63b57cc3c918fcdbb903546447ee81825764e3e75dd5"}, {"expression": "systèmes cryptographiques", "span": [427, 452], "weight": null, "norm": "systèmes cryptographiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:f31a82ebb48526a4e5f20e9d70b55a3660ed7a85520d1ad2cc9be202819d06a5"}, {"expression": "protocoles de chiffrement quantique", "span": [533, 568], "weight": null, "norm": "protocoles de chiffrement quantique", "embedding_ref": "emb:2bc39f2f3fbd588d856f2a579dda59bacdaa874325cfbaffc4c337baaa4e2b14"}, {"expression": "mécanique quantique", "span": [613, 632], "weight": null, "norm": "mécanique quantique", "embedding_ref": "emb:401a3c847f61458b707c87650c3914db3001cfd180963c963dd32b00db27fb28"}, {"expression": "ordinateurs quantiques", "span": [653, 675], "weight": null, "norm": "ordinateurs quantiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:17191a3d07e80eed337ab6ca5467923057f2cb800e91015c46b7b4ea557cd5f8"}, {"expression": "développement d'ordinateurs quantiques", "span": [637, 675], "weight": null, "norm": "développement d'ordinateurs quantiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:16fc6a401062569fd369284148a73c9b6c5abe389e06cc55a2439c8000468e4d"}, {"expression": "décohérence", "span": [740, 751], "weight": null, "norm": "décohérence", "embedding_ref": "emb:3ac4c1ce3c735e382e3838d45a06bdb67956c83630b42e7a0a490ab20b898b84"}, {"expression": "systèmes", "span": [427, 435], "weight": null, "norm": "systèmes", "embedding_ref": "emb:6ea2df4f15ecab697dc4a615a57c0bd2a2f383328862b26c0af884c9b6df3b92"}, {"expression": "laboratoires", "span": [839, 851], "weight": null, "norm": "laboratoires", "embedding_ref": "emb:02701c3fea6505cfc1ac3a3128bd16e86316484fd8ff4cb4ab969494fefe511e"}, {"expression": "entreprises technologiques", "span": [859, 885], "weight": null, "norm": "entreprises technologiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:4683069e30340d247c1c283bdcc685e6fc82584ade8cf90c3b7a9fca7e220421"}, {"expression": "secteurs", "span": [946, 954], "weight": null, "norm": "secteurs", "embedding_ref": "emb:8eec2494c87e100bc79e491cf7750719a7f0c961413dd62b9b88e1bf764ecdbc"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 7, "source_expression": "mécanique quantique"}}}], "warning": null}
