{"status": "ok", "tool": "search_text", "message": "Recherche semantique executee.", "query": "les sumériens écrivaient-ils des romans", "summary": {"collection_name": "secretarius_semantic_graph", "query_count": 2, "hit_lists": 2, "top_k": 10, "min_score": 0.75, "keyword_query_count": 0}, "documents": [{"id": 4291910312149135398, "score": 0.9082289338111877, "combined_score": 0.9582289338111878, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:32595ccb39b3b52326e3dc1633e39cd6a2ff9b6663de281d0d266cf14240b032", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://archives-litteraires.fr/liaisons-dangereuses-1782"], "url": "https://archives-litteraires.fr/liaisons-dangereuses-1782", "source_id": "src:a1443bf7f6f810f03dd9f16e8421f1c3ad94008329387d3e1041e774ca600ce5"}, "content": {"text": "Le roman épistolaire, forme narrative constituée d'une suite de lettres, connaît son apogée au siècle des Lumières. Il permet une immersion directe dans la psychologie des personnages et offre une vision fragmentée et subjective des événements. L'absence de narrateur omniscient crée un suspense particulier, le lecteur devant reconstituer l'intrigue à travers des points de vue partiels et parfois contradictoires. Cette forme exige une grande maîtrise de la voix et du style de chaque épistolier, faisant du roman une mosaïque de discours et de tensions sociales.", "hash": "sha256:62197426de103760d4b6ef3183be6453555dcb70920c84ed52a666dc8c3c8b9d"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "Les Liaisons dangereuses", "document_date": "15-03-1782", "keywords": ["#roman", "#lettres", "#XVIIIe_siècle"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:37:57Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:37:47Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:302618bcc124b3e1c037c1757820e188ab88a6d7d091efda24e9bba9c40914e2", "start": 0, "end": 565, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "roman épistolaire", "span": [3, 20], "weight": null, "norm": "roman épistolaire", "embedding_ref": "emb:2eaa997201c929d1916605b057fa7a526f27665d394405648d77ce77bf96c796"}, {"expression": "forme narrative", "span": [22, 37], "weight": null, "norm": "forme narrative", "embedding_ref": "emb:0eb373127dabe8b657137a0fd9a0d2ea74b7e5210dfdfbdb6aeffd6d85542180"}, {"expression": "suite de lettres", "span": [55, 71], "weight": null, "norm": "suite de lettres", "embedding_ref": "emb:53ab05b1bc577402ed952bceab47dfcdd292fd1a78d1e13c666fc51179698954"}, {"expression": "apogée", "span": [85, 91], "weight": null, "norm": "apogée", "embedding_ref": "emb:97a67fb704b8449a841f21cc859ea740a2218a086528b91722846105c1407ff5"}, {"expression": "siècle des Lumières", "span": [95, 114], "weight": null, "norm": "siècle des lumières", "embedding_ref": "emb:3f8d987d3b17ba40533dd9621dfea831190d8d63bb1725085ec47b7338136a7d"}, {"expression": "psychologie des personnages", "span": [156, 183], "weight": null, "norm": "psychologie des personnages", "embedding_ref": "emb:03d80728b9aa42fecd332cc05bfdb9340b016782295b464b7b0f8260a32a680e"}, {"expression": "vision fragmentée", "span": [197, 214], "weight": null, "norm": "vision fragmentée", "embedding_ref": "emb:d9415bb4e6750bf14be3efcee1295d88ee2b847cbcaf3b102719e2076ead38cd"}, {"expression": "événements", "span": [233, 243], "weight": null, "norm": "événements", "embedding_ref": "emb:ff15f2423c36f946230624bb55225be369431951961a57b73123172b09047361"}, {"expression": "narrateur omniscient", "span": [258, 278], "weight": null, "norm": "narrateur omniscient", "embedding_ref": "emb:540582aff3bd2dacb4591d3a39ac9e272754c5ce94878543d96e32e2e6c2c2be"}, {"expression": "suspense particulier", "span": [287, 307], "weight": null, "norm": "suspense particulier", "embedding_ref": "emb:e9b32498476d25d05838f9004eb8645fda1ce629762b94c9026331f1e201877d"}, {"expression": "intrigue", "span": [342, 350], "weight": null, "norm": "intrigue", "embedding_ref": "emb:56c411638a2bebe277659a837bf6a29487f1e00f88d9cff44ff2421c39e3497b"}, {"expression": "points de vue partiels", "span": [365, 387], "weight": null, "norm": "points de vue partiels", "embedding_ref": "emb:8ebf623baba28f1caca00dd2564c88f5e615d35b8c20bb1f6f752ac2ce759768"}, {"expression": "roman", "span": [3, 8], "weight": null, "norm": "roman", "embedding_ref": "emb:8d3309558539008b2cd1ec25454899670f96d46313992c1b380c29ada4fb891d"}, {"expression": "mosaïque de discours", "span": [520, 540], "weight": null, "norm": "mosaïque de discours", "embedding_ref": "emb:83e3a1265307f3e0c1e80db30e8cf8b9ea784058e7984a3c44cf9afeac3b5dbe"}, {"expression": "tensions sociales", "span": [547, 564], "weight": null, "norm": "tensions sociales", "embedding_ref": "emb:4fd6782ad86f50665e5533858a2b11ae6d14f6bdec4ca61d350023a5b9b01601"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 12, "source_expression": "roman"}}}, {"id": 4036472102459064604, "score": 0.8863388895988464, "combined_score": 0.9363388895988465, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:56a7cbe1c5d363310852ec6ad89271080f3f09b5cc0efb17da1b2f0ab865655f", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:5a7d59723d1cf53b05cc19e766216e75f24a148326b4cffc688cf8e3396cd248"}, "content": {"text": "Les utopies technologiques ont toujours fasciné l'humanité. Elles proposent un avenir où la technologie résout tous les problèmes, élimine la souffrance et crée une société parfaite. Des cités idéales aux intelligences artificielles bienveillantes, ces visions mêlent innovation et espoir. Pourtant, elles soulèvent aussi des questions éthiques et pratiques. La promesse d'un monde meilleur grâce aux machines coexiste avec le risque de dépendance, de surveillance et d'inégalités. Ces récits, qu'ils soient littéraires ou philosophiques, nous invitent à réfléchir à la direction que prend notre progrès. Ils nous rappellent que chaque avancée porte en elle un choix de société. L'utopie n'est peut-être pas un lieu, mais un chemin à construire, avec prudence et humanité.", "hash": "sha256:1ba3769f2360e4e4d8b654264a2b253e0ba10f916c88ebf52a75061dbb098760"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "Les utopies technologiques : entre rêve et réalité", "keywords": ["#technologie", "#utopie", "#avenir"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:33:21Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:33:06Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:54023f33be2b6838af23fa32286108dabd14f05631641b628f60e3cb34d0f3c9", "start": 0, "end": 772, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "utopies technologiques", "span": [4, 26], "weight": null, "norm": "utopies technologiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:99d9f09824104f67a3d0ca15d857cf30f14b27b579d14510ad8e78c0cb8616b7"}, {"expression": "avenir", "span": [79, 85], "weight": null, "norm": "avenir", "embedding_ref": "emb:8eaa565f677e430f4f940c5c8320bf22257c613583b40809a30116fb4a07c2c4"}, {"expression": "technologie", "span": [92, 103], "weight": null, "norm": "technologie", "embedding_ref": "emb:4f1478c87f8c6efcfc10fbefa32799f1447e32345bb7754e5c887f604d72fcd1"}, {"expression": "problèmes", "span": [120, 129], "weight": null, "norm": "problèmes", "embedding_ref": "emb:023de8b311a45c3ff23a419561d461d8dcc082bd1904befca37e3dc7c12b526d"}, {"expression": "société parfaite", "span": [165, 181], "weight": null, "norm": "société parfaite", "embedding_ref": "emb:a1c589e840a1e00fd02f548bfbc8be091b7650580f2babd8141c084ad919900f"}, {"expression": "cités idéales", "span": [187, 200], "weight": null, "norm": "cités idéales", "embedding_ref": "emb:ca15e3ab149bccd63e0d0c25ce5b0ad9eb1c2cf40302a27c94767fd6c95a94fb"}, {"expression": "intelligences artificielles", "span": [205, 232], "weight": null, "norm": "intelligences artificielles", "embedding_ref": "emb:fe313a7943b1bd168b532173e691a8c7a2f460917654f9efdfe6435a39022993"}, {"expression": "questions éthiques", "span": [326, 344], "weight": null, "norm": "questions éthiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:793c3d2b026f0bc83c9878bb1a869cc141ee963d3f17810d6ea7d2aecac91461"}, {"expression": "promesse d'un monde meilleur", "span": [362, 390], "weight": null, "norm": "promesse d'un monde meilleur", "embedding_ref": "emb:6a04c12087c7513e611a4ed1a452ff42b5f877ded4935142f83aeeb2a2c5236f"}, {"expression": "machines", "span": [401, 409], "weight": null, "norm": "machines", "embedding_ref": "emb:9909c6ffff1d613ef1c841d69102a0e9ee718ff275ce99e51f4b8d845583747f"}, {"expression": "risque de dépendance", "span": [427, 447], "weight": null, "norm": "risque de dépendance", "embedding_ref": "emb:66ae4393ecd9c04ba78e0646398e3342cd1fb80d55cf7fb96e559fff56cf4c5f"}, {"expression": "surveillance", "span": [452, 464], "weight": null, "norm": "surveillance", "embedding_ref": "emb:5745bfdc728dc097190088dfe16cb35bbc31dfd8e68604002ae8525fe11be531"}, {"expression": "inégalités", "span": [470, 480], "weight": null, "norm": "inégalités", "embedding_ref": "emb:cb76cebf840ffe3ece1353745c0ecc500c7fab15c91e677021016ea09afd83bb"}, {"expression": "récits", "span": [486, 492], "weight": null, "norm": "récits", "embedding_ref": "emb:ae269a27e453ff0ef637fdfa168d4b4f44c0e1b4fc09f20df30c573e44d1cefa"}, {"expression": "littéraires", "span": [508, 519], "weight": null, "norm": "littéraires", "embedding_ref": "emb:87cb6415d2cf0fe4351d46613fce318327d4587934d3a703d69dd022320922f4"}, {"expression": "philosophiques", "span": [523, 537], "weight": null, "norm": "philosophiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:b6c02742ba93898c10b3b4c86356f5e5ad65082ff0edd81adda20e7b8c500235"}, {"expression": "direction", "span": [570, 579], "weight": null, "norm": "direction", "embedding_ref": "emb:76d7eceb53c825e7a5d8ff773e08480fe19a64414c4770cbc4df5772fb8e76eb"}, {"expression": "progrès", "span": [596, 603], "weight": null, "norm": "progrès", "embedding_ref": "emb:783460db732f460d48e5dda2dcf34f79f26183cd65266c8e7a9210cf1464bf8f"}, {"expression": "choix de société", "span": [661, 677], "weight": null, "norm": "choix de société", "embedding_ref": "emb:2a4f5bbc5a86a7e582f2e527501576467dd146dc25911f10660e41ed5fd47bca"}, {"expression": "utopie", "span": [4, 10], "weight": null, "norm": "utopie", "embedding_ref": "emb:9c341dea9ee3402b7106a52d9ba510a91b46864ee61df651f5fd0d456239ddce"}, {"expression": "lieu", "span": [711, 715], "weight": null, "norm": "lieu", "embedding_ref": "emb:0b5a287ccbd288a8c52f745b0437081ba1b8e47335c08e79b8c57ac3f0074a01"}, {"expression": "chemin à construire", "span": [725, 744], "weight": null, "norm": "chemin à construire", "embedding_ref": "emb:32dd98310484c3527086a0870b21b3c5509f385e43e5415987b250d713ddaeca"}, {"expression": "prudence", "span": [751, 759], "weight": null, "norm": "prudence", "embedding_ref": "emb:d2e599e3ea66eb0a9ddb77feab08713db2690b1830ac2b8dd219efa30d1a0650"}, {"expression": "humanité", "span": [50, 58], "weight": null, "norm": "humanité", "embedding_ref": "emb:36296978d74047de7aaf159485d9d391f7b281fa9e52e7a6d93af1cab3685916"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 14, "source_expression": "littéraires"}}}, {"id": 7903731975264360047, "score": 0.8803719282150269, "combined_score": 0.9303719282150269, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:c50dffef196395e46dd8622dae37b748ac72fa807a69645b83e10339d52a245e", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:071f8f36a3934d39935dbc15dfc7f4419f1c8515d48912141ef1851e27d1fc6d"}, "content": {"text": "L'écriture est née de la nécessité de fixer la pensée et de transmettre l'information au-delà de l'oralité. Les premières traces apparaissent en Mésopotamie avec l'écriture cunéiforme, suivie des hiéroglyphes égyptiens. Chaque civilisation a développé son propre système, des idéogrammes chinois à l'alphabet phénicien, ancêtre de la plupart des écritures modernes. Cette invention a fondamentalement transformé les sociétés, permettant l'administration, la littérature et la préservation du savoir à travers les siècles.", "hash": "sha256:b02a251b296a0361b408c481354ade62379d0a92f6c62ce460845fd07d17b62d"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L'évolution des systèmes d'écriture", "document_date": "15-03-2023", "keywords": ["#écriture", "#histoire", "#civilisation"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:27Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:19Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:02f156e3eab86c2ba3e6ab70b567447119c87f9c6500280ef50f005c16c74288", "start": 0, "end": 521, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "écriture", "span": [2, 10], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture", "embedding_ref": "emb:14dbf2140003b3f9514a659dcfea18b7a8d252a0f73f1e06db724bf87aa0bbd2"}, {"expression": "Mésopotamie", "span": [145, 156], "weight": null, "norm": "mésopotamie", "embedding_ref": "emb:2161e2cb7e9e0bd12679781125917bc1873f48cbc720ba6ceed40bde80745a5d"}, {"expression": "écriture cunéiforme", "span": [164, 183], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture cunéiforme", "embedding_ref": "emb:da96b1f5f39adf551773eed24f7636dc2fa2787977e0f730db56bccb2d9a9442"}, {"expression": "hiéroglyphes égyptiens", "span": [196, 218], "weight": null, "norm": "hiéroglyphes égyptiens", "embedding_ref": "emb:c9a27a0e76526f9e12cc5929a98a2e948f391980919e316c0e6a94fb3382d574"}, {"expression": "idéogrammes chinois", "span": [276, 295], "weight": null, "norm": "idéogrammes chinois", "embedding_ref": "emb:09f8d4f312d050a8084b3973d7d99b0407344f32b3102cc19cf91b94378d5dfd"}, {"expression": "alphabet phénicien", "span": [300, 318], "weight": null, "norm": "alphabet phénicien", "embedding_ref": "emb:4b68e41be67918155cec3c7139bd1b88e3ad1f88b17deca64bd9fa9027b214d9"}, {"expression": "écritures modernes", "span": [346, 364], "weight": null, "norm": "écritures modernes", "embedding_ref": "emb:2f3c4fb0a87bb7f6009abd1ce1dd748ee78ace1cbcc0053ab86fc31195f32559"}, {"expression": "administration", "span": [439, 453], "weight": null, "norm": "administration", "embedding_ref": "emb:28f3ac334055784782b32060aa6aa3d1fcd6c8942f41fea07630f29c8eb0352e"}, {"expression": "littérature", "span": [458, 469], "weight": null, "norm": "littérature", "embedding_ref": "emb:3f74484df1a2eb2f9ac82a971c3f782cfa9a1a134042d9c9d7696ec8767b5575"}, {"expression": "préservation du savoir", "span": [476, 498], "weight": null, "norm": "préservation du savoir", "embedding_ref": "emb:d2fc6f73ab8168ff2090a2426cee06a5650fe7c28c0bb5f733f91aa165e9d7d8"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 8, "source_expression": "littérature"}}}, {"id": 6795407700323786393, "score": 0.7956767082214355, "combined_score": 0.8456767082214356, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:a5262ed0d170e3566b60979f25bc333acb0fcac90f4f4dc8d7f4d72dfe1407cd", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:e6418123538e55bf6d5f56922bd70aff4e8392689e0c5069fffa4f7b44725e67"}, "content": {"text": "L'idée d'un monde transformé par la technologie a toujours habité l'imaginaire collectif. Des cités futuristes de la science-fiction aux promesses contemporaines de l'intelligence artificielle et de la réalité virtuelle, les utopies technologiques proposent une vision d'un avenir où les machines résoudraient les grands maux de l'humanité : la maladie, la pénurie, la fatigue, voire la mort elle-même. Ces récits, souvent portés par des figures charismatiques ou des mouvements idéologiques, mélangent progrès scientifique et aspiration à une société plus juste, plus efficace, et libérée des contraintes matérielles.\n\nPourtant, l'histoire récente nous invite à la nuance. Chaque avancée majeure – l'ère numérique, les biotechnologies, l'hyperconnectivité – s'accompagne de son lot de désillusions. Les promesses d'un loisir universel grâce à l'automatisation se heurtent à la précarisation de certains emplois. Les espaces numériques, conçus comme des agoras démocratiques, peuvent devenir des chambres d'écho ou des outils de surveillance. L'utopie se fissure alors, laissant place à la dystopie, son ombre portée.\n\nLe véritable enjeu n'est peut-être pas de réaliser l'utopie, mais de conserver sa fonction critique. Elle agit comme une boussole, fixant un horizon de désirs et de valeurs. La question n'est plus \"la technologie nous rendra-t-elle parfaits ?\" mais \"quelle société voulons-nous construire avec elle ?\". En ce sens, les utopies technologiques, même inatteignables, restent indispensables. Elles nous forcent à interroger le présent et à orienter l'innovation non pas vers un destin écrit d'avance, mais vers un choix collectif et constamment révisé.", "hash": "sha256:ebcb778cf27b9b0484c43685ff05f5a2ee7abd2ef38a1b9f5079a0ab163b1ee3"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "Les utopies technologiques : entre rêve et réalité", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:36:01Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:35:38Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:afb24b0eed2a0effaa11d56565eb935fbb003bf56fec7e49a6408f28b2dd89d3", "start": 0, "end": 1041, "text_ref": null}, {"chunk_id": "chunk:c03ae5f2070a8878bab027f58c32a21e0a5cd0115fb1ea1879fec6aa4a509c96", "start": 1041, "end": 1908, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "utopies technologiques", "span": [225, 247], "weight": null, "norm": "utopies technologiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:7ed07863a32db929dfa7c6c91d0c8a4561112ba18cef461ea429d4137e9d81a6"}, {"expression": "promesses contemporaines", "span": [137, 161], "weight": null, "norm": "promesses contemporaines", "embedding_ref": "emb:eba9ddc34f7330457cad8d4dcc0fb42cfd68cb3706f3e516c88b646882594f91"}, {"expression": "intelligence artificielle", "span": [167, 192], "weight": null, "norm": "intelligence artificielle", "embedding_ref": "emb:49433cee328f81e204c7994900b7d20b005155312080eb7278d1f4cf5aaa0c81"}, {"expression": "réalité virtuelle", "span": [202, 219], "weight": null, "norm": "réalité virtuelle", "embedding_ref": "emb:ae762221c4643e2e4dce6801a96b907363920d60efbda10f25939f121a90f4f1"}, {"expression": "grands maux de l'humanité", "span": [314, 339], "weight": null, "norm": "grands maux de l'humanité", "embedding_ref": "emb:04707e4b8663ce7dba4efc2eddb08355e1576407dc74752a896ea47759a81135"}, {"expression": "promesses d'un loisir universel", "span": [804, 835], "weight": null, "norm": "promesses d'un loisir universel", "embedding_ref": "emb:b2334bd3b314a47e5bb102eb1a2fd4a3a9108ac5955d219ae2fccc71116f2591"}, {"expression": "automatisation", "span": [846, 860], "weight": null, "norm": "automatisation", "embedding_ref": "emb:7739eb07c7de957889c34e5ca252b5909804fff6f01ca26b97f70ce9f7377672"}, {"expression": "espaces numériques", "span": [917, 935], "weight": null, "norm": "espaces numériques", "embedding_ref": "emb:aa3c8e07009904ab7cb0722aa8d13707181d2bec0d49ced5de18b64c4eb72cb3"}, {"expression": "agoras démocratiques", "span": [954, 974], "weight": null, "norm": "agoras démocratiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:2b0a982381711ce12ab069cd2b3bc30fd3e2e55cb259cd5a1c69947d00a1ec5d"}, {"expression": "chambres d'écho", "span": [996, 1011], "weight": null, "norm": "chambres d'écho", "embedding_ref": "emb:f28e9203d786a360db03d176d8aaf68eef91338e49a446c6c9483ac015e5c064"}, {"expression": "outils de surveillance", "span": [1019, 1041], "weight": null, "norm": "outils de surveillance", "embedding_ref": "emb:2453958aa1b014bb05f28d2dcbaef4d7e1e4da63ae2afdb4849377b44ef2899f"}, {"expression": "l'automatisation", "span": [844, 860], "weight": null, "norm": "l'automatisation", "embedding_ref": "emb:0edb8d9fbd7c99dc17b7d16196ae66712a8a0e939dcce2fb33b6724b37d810fc"}, {"expression": "dystopie", "span": [1090, 1098], "weight": null, "norm": "dystopie", "embedding_ref": "emb:1840d61d9f07cd765c8a7cc96fed544b8fbe82a215574901181714f27ab53354"}, {"expression": "fonction critique", "span": [1201, 1218], "weight": null, "norm": "fonction critique", "embedding_ref": "emb:a312e0cdced2d0e0cecdbbc96a37b6712f2ec7ed31cb0e61ef0717a11ac77e93"}, {"expression": "horizon de désirs et de valeurs", "span": [1260, 1291], "weight": null, "norm": "horizon de désirs et de valeurs", "embedding_ref": "emb:c1b37529c504dd619f1ef0488198458d22f55209087d44a307d0585fd87cb550"}, {"expression": "société", "span": [544, 551], "weight": null, "norm": "société", "embedding_ref": "emb:b231b971bee8603bdb84672a31312bac1e0eeba270bae8502b45ae102a3d70ed"}, {"expression": "choix collectif", "span": [1629, 1644], "weight": null, "norm": "choix collectif", "embedding_ref": "emb:28d2f2fb8ef109058069b31b742e9c125210a13738f210f46d30820535cd74b8"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 15, "source_expression": "société"}}}, {"id": 4223214503270020719, "score": 0.8267577290534973, "combined_score": 0.8267577290534973, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:dfe802c2db277ddd8a2506ad30e53ca174929e142ee19d5dda70e5ff603d1fa8", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://www.lettres-classiques.fr/roman-epistolaire-histoire"], "url": "https://www.lettres-classiques.fr/roman-epistolaire-histoire", "source_id": "src:6f27acdf362742e353facd2dd48e8b127b4a118bda57abd19f1296d68fe6227d"}, "content": {"text": "Le roman épistolaire trouve ses racines dans l'Antiquité, mais c'est au XVIIIe siècle qu'il connaît son âge d'or. Cette forme narrative, construite entièrement à partir de lettres échangées entre les personnages, offre une immersion unique dans leur psychologie. L'absence de narrateur omniscient crée un effet de réel et de subjectivité, le lecteur devant reconstituer l'intrigue à travers des points de vue partiels et parfois contradictoires. Des œuvres comme *Les Liaisons dangereuses* de Laclos exploitent magistralement ce procédé pour dépeindre les jeux de pouvoir et de séduction. La forme épistolaire permet aussi une grande variété de tons, de la confidence intime à la polémique philosophique, faisant de chaque missive un révélateur de caractère et un moteur de l'action.", "hash": "sha256:0385957c458698189085d6b5f212107ec92e408d61a54530fe58db696fee65ed"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "Le roman épistolaire trouve ses racines...", "document_date": "12-05-2024", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:27:52Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:27:39Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:3b1c596c1e80891c1e96c8aae96a63249ed66b26d525d3322d713c0f43853129", "start": 0, "end": 783, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "roman épistolaire", "span": [3, 20], "weight": null, "norm": "roman épistolaire", "embedding_ref": "emb:3abc7f756822ec05acf5c0cd8e0f2e42f1afbe51673757af8515f00b4cbbfa77"}, {"expression": "Antiquité", "span": [47, 56], "weight": null, "norm": "antiquité", "embedding_ref": "emb:e2403527720d2043f6c052759408efa29d8150c0cb2bcd0b41b182c144d9a40f"}, {"expression": "XVIIIe siècle", "span": [72, 85], "weight": null, "norm": "xviiie siècle", "embedding_ref": "emb:e24475bce1746fb848a078f194fa8ae899f1759b45d4470f6a999ca3cb7c7cb9"}, {"expression": "âge d'or", "span": [104, 112], "weight": null, "norm": "âge d'or", "embedding_ref": "emb:1191f4bbbafbf83ae396ac761a44022ee5f90cb44ac7ad82b98db1c3a615fad7"}, {"expression": "forme narrative", "span": [120, 135], "weight": null, "norm": "forme narrative", "embedding_ref": "emb:b3dfaebe9b0b944b2b565690736eb40f7ab8aa7e97cd6de5e0aaf760b69b08e0"}, {"expression": "lettres échangées", "span": [172, 189], "weight": null, "norm": "lettres échangées", "embedding_ref": "emb:7f1932438afb2aad715ab6f50562985ac65c10c68c0e4a3fe430f4944c0c0f68"}, {"expression": "psychologie", "span": [250, 261], "weight": null, "norm": "psychologie", "embedding_ref": "emb:b08c4065e1caa5282db5e07aadbc75b5caf570d10ad95d874ad7292d1197bb04"}, {"expression": "narrateur omniscient", "span": [276, 296], "weight": null, "norm": "narrateur omniscient", "embedding_ref": "emb:a9ef5e16ae38e7b0490bc00bd147098348b9ec248cc496e6b3252c81ef06564b"}, {"expression": "Les Liaisons dangereuses", "span": [464, 488], "weight": null, "norm": "les liaisons dangereuses", "embedding_ref": "emb:189e116599fa0401242124f2e542b4dfc305bb24e873874e629fc9d7d75d25da"}, {"expression": "Laclos", "span": [493, 499], "weight": null, "norm": "laclos", "embedding_ref": "emb:478cb14727cd2f80e07456d66baf4334380f93f3343a56d4cfef33a7b4a58658"}, {"expression": "jeux de pouvoir", "span": [556, 571], "weight": null, "norm": "jeux de pouvoir", "embedding_ref": "emb:9ecf6f35c081c760a5a4f4c906947943b16ff5f848aa4c9210e338d00b70fc79"}, {"expression": "séduction", "span": [578, 587], "weight": null, "norm": "séduction", "embedding_ref": "emb:a628871cd58c74b25026d0244f78903ad8877434dedc10ee4db405350deb0628"}, {"expression": "forme épistolaire", "span": [592, 609], "weight": null, "norm": "forme épistolaire", "embedding_ref": "emb:a66a60e8c0d33616619364afff15e3f738f75059a5dc1ffe45cd30d7b2f166fa"}, {"expression": "ton", "span": [645, 648], "weight": null, "norm": "ton", "embedding_ref": "emb:565b4698fb5de1a47297e47fba47e348752c4990f44bc1bce34c2358d66275c1"}, {"expression": "confidence intime", "span": [657, 674], "weight": null, "norm": "confidence intime", "embedding_ref": "emb:72d14b5b5ab63f1aa2e544771b9d11254b9bf9eafa315db4cefb5b02ef083692"}, {"expression": "polémique philosophique", "span": [680, 703], "weight": null, "norm": "polémique philosophique", "embedding_ref": "emb:03a20d76cd26f30bd8b148d994ab7ffa981204b4d3eaacb0fb4fd3ae91e8e0be"}, {"expression": "missive", "span": [723, 730], "weight": null, "norm": "missive", "embedding_ref": "emb:07935b2882fec77244fa299fab20deb3fe5ac4d5e0a7d679ad70d95057168dbf"}, {"expression": "caractère", "span": [748, 757], "weight": null, "norm": "caractère", "embedding_ref": "emb:754b6b2480c5a52bd85ec45de93333c6982c2391541fcd738c5f79cf62136b31"}, {"expression": "moteur de l'action", "span": [764, 782], "weight": null, "norm": "moteur de l'action", "embedding_ref": "emb:bd0bb272c50bb7b387dc0438b7ad61e4b6b6aa4fa6ab72a9d8433728dacb1fa1"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 0, "source_expression": "roman épistolaire"}}}, {"id": 6295617482203594535, "score": 0.7746433019638062, "combined_score": 0.8246433019638062, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:2b77acd3c4941f82c38f2465a9ca4ccc9d04a454252db72b6e9140714495638d", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://www.ethologie-cognitive.org/conscience-animale"], "url": "https://www.ethologie-cognitive.org/conscience-animale", "source_id": "src:fe348c5c6e3e11d0648f4b3325544fe4bc130d514aae7defaef2c2d961f20e14"}, "content": {"text": "La question de la conscience chez les animaux demeure un sujet de débat intense en éthologie et en philosophie. De nombreuses études sur les corvidés, les céphalopodes ou les grands mammifères suggèrent des capacités de représentation de soi, d'anticipation et même d'empathie. L'observation de comportements de deuil, de tromperie ou d'utilisation d'outils complexe alimente l'hypothèse d'une forme de vie intérieure. Cependant, l'accès à cette subjectivité reste un défi méthodologique majeur, laissant souvent la place à des interprétations anthropomorphiques. La frontière entre cognition avancée et conscience phénoménale reste floue, invitant à une profonde humilité épistémologique.", "hash": "sha256:3961c0e174c9835134d287986d0d7e2f5a577e4b32d053fde482786f45e7f2eb"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "La question de la conscience chez les...", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:38:10Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:37:58Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:7dc9df6b3f59bc7ca330d6338fd6910796965a9f9bc48badb289f81263a0642c", "start": 0, "end": 689, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "conscience chez les animaux", "span": [18, 45], "weight": null, "norm": "conscience chez les animaux", "embedding_ref": "emb:0b575545339443f67f5e9a846fb869e57b844678e0f867a1357c9177ccf5396e"}, {"expression": "éthologie", "span": [83, 92], "weight": null, "norm": "éthologie", "embedding_ref": "emb:990c3cc7852cbafd844a66fd8a7139093a3c3ac36246bee5a8256409eb352a5c"}, {"expression": "philosophie", "span": [99, 110], "weight": null, "norm": "philosophie", "embedding_ref": "emb:fce6bf75f6423adabc6cb56895ddf1425896fe0f3daa901eb253f353aeaed293"}, {"expression": "corvidés", "span": [141, 149], "weight": null, "norm": "corvidés", "embedding_ref": "emb:3151f0e6cac76f797f2caf01a17e8ecdb75755d7fa13208db25ef7b7555e0e57"}, {"expression": "céphalopodes", "span": [155, 167], "weight": null, "norm": "céphalopodes", "embedding_ref": "emb:84d1f5a9967d697492a8f053f49c7f01fc7a208297f1995a2c58afb231187500"}, {"expression": "grands mammifères", "span": [175, 192], "weight": null, "norm": "grands mammifères", "embedding_ref": "emb:92914a0bafbb5ae40ab6f054f17fc009940aa0e2054bba100fdbf1c68f0757f1"}, {"expression": "capacités de représentation de soi", "span": [207, 241], "weight": null, "norm": "capacités de représentation de soi", "embedding_ref": "emb:11a2a6e6f835abb73712e21fcb38602bd4b8f4f21a51706094ef43955fa96568"}, {"expression": "anticipation", "span": [245, 257], "weight": null, "norm": "anticipation", "embedding_ref": "emb:ce0cc46d1fcb7b09258cc5260c0349c078ef7aed5703c16388f77a62a239a9c7"}, {"expression": "comportements de deuil", "span": [295, 317], "weight": null, "norm": "comportements de deuil", "embedding_ref": "emb:3f85178e9f3f77dd46e29d77ff7790642c0c4c2ee429263ab6fa8607e25f6fe5"}, {"expression": "tromperie", "span": [322, 331], "weight": null, "norm": "tromperie", "embedding_ref": "emb:3ca357996ba43defd9ba81537dbe06de5bb31b8447c4dcbe0aa2bf4908c17901"}, {"expression": "outils complexe", "span": [351, 366], "weight": null, "norm": "outils complexe", "embedding_ref": "emb:5b3a664e0968ef31c3a6507fd46119cb156122ef9813f55780c860f704cd0f5b"}, {"expression": "forme de vie intérieure", "span": [394, 417], "weight": null, "norm": "forme de vie intérieure", "embedding_ref": "emb:604f72da04fc9ba64aaf755ef32db55cc41cdcced1c0e01ce51764d4d9510653"}, {"expression": "subjectivité", "span": [446, 458], "weight": null, "norm": "subjectivité", "embedding_ref": "emb:91c659a0aa0fc71b863746d07f18be31561cf6fafe1ffc8c4fb2b0d4da34cf6f"}, {"expression": "cognition avancée", "span": [583, 600], "weight": null, "norm": "cognition avancée", "embedding_ref": "emb:7f717eafdd2a0cd2571b8760f894fab3fbf6c58a090c6477fd65780608589854"}, {"expression": "conscience phénoménale", "span": [604, 626], "weight": null, "norm": "conscience phénoménale", "embedding_ref": "emb:72c764794591962458295cf816678be39ce9c52024c5f76085a33abd8c5cf1ca"}, {"expression": "humilité épistémologique", "span": [664, 688], "weight": null, "norm": "humilité épistémologique", "embedding_ref": "emb:41b7967b4142000570bf17f047614207a90f8a9a999c92b39bef69df27d42984"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 1, "source_expression": "éthologie"}}}, {"id": 7568968890382800977, "score": 0.8148695230484009, "combined_score": 0.8148695230484009, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:e1d2e044f07156bf4b14252a1e83521e5bd838de1f78a4d438545bfb0fe6fe77", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:0517dfbc6e3bd4373cb8d67ff0a3daf661602d4952dbb0617334894637ef9fd2"}, "content": {"text": "L’incendie de Rome en 64 après J.-C. est l’un des événements les plus marquants de l’Antiquité. Il a ravagé une grande partie de la ville pendant six jours et sept nuits, détruisant des quartiers entiers. Les causes restent débattues : accident ou incendie criminel ? L’empereur Néron, souvent accusé, aurait même chanté pendant le désastre selon la légende. La reconstruction qui a suivi a transformé l’urbanisme de Rome, avec des rues plus larges et des bâtiments en pierre. Ce sinistre a laissé une empreinte durable dans l’histoire et la culture occidentale.", "hash": "sha256:9a95bcdd46c57ab81e8b5c641182d7273ee98dda07ea83cf15aaee3a59011942"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L’incendie de Rome en 64 après J.-C....", "document_date": "19-07-0064", "keywords": ["#Rome", "#incendie", "#Néron", "#histoire", "#catastrophe"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:39:54Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:39:46Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:65f328e4959fd9d0fe608715703d7857875ef1342bd06a8e246b1e16486a563a", "start": 0, "end": 562, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "incendie de Rome", "span": [2, 18], "weight": null, "norm": "incendie de rome", "embedding_ref": "emb:f89f063c12f4df75dcd641b6a3972d549bc94738aae5587333d5d8f5aeb91b65"}, {"expression": "64 après J.-C.", "span": [22, 36], "weight": null, "norm": "64 après j.-c.", "embedding_ref": "emb:e2042eae9ff9453b833939a263c00283b86c1c706e61c01a8ce18b50ce56fea5"}, {"expression": "l’Antiquité", "span": [83, 94], "weight": null, "norm": "l’antiquité", "embedding_ref": "emb:bb22fb8d8249df240558b118f4d0e39dcde2284d5d7f01d9ea71e5d3eac95d88"}, {"expression": "l’urbanisme de Rome", "span": [402, 421], "weight": null, "norm": "l’urbanisme de rome", "embedding_ref": "emb:ed7a1410b313859ff9153d7e2589c2bbb0084c10c501fcd5c01797161e7ad4c7"}, {"expression": "l’histoire et la culture occidentale", "span": [525, 561], "weight": null, "norm": "l’histoire et la culture occidentale", "embedding_ref": "emb:dde4cb1eb776de50ca1d6653bfdd1443503fd7d743971b26a2e76fd69e62603c"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 2, "source_expression": "l’Antiquité"}}}, {"id": 8709804221220511036, "score": 0.8080592155456543, "combined_score": 0.8080592155456543, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:94b0f5e5aa85052d28111caa2198195db8498a53c5762f620200b1b76ee7f422", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://www.histoire-romaine.fr/incendies-rome"], "url": "https://www.histoire-romaine.fr/incendies-rome", "source_id": "src:65a9e5ee9451c8ae2401e397dc33d6c861beef2ff49fca1784995ed0a95325a4"}, "content": {"text": "L'incendie de Rome en 64 apr. J.-C. reste l'un des événements les plus marquants de l'Antiquité. Parti des boutiques entourant le Grand Cirque, le feu se propagea rapidement à travers les ruelles étroites et les immeubles de bois de la ville. Il fit rage pendant six jours et sept nuits, détruisant trois des quatorze régions de Rome entièrement et en endommageant gravement sept autres. Les rumeurs accusèrent l'empereur Néron lui-même d'avoir ordonné l'incendie pour libérer de l'espace et construire son nouveau palais, la Domus Aurea. Bien que ces accusations soient largement considérées comme des calomnies propagées par ses ennemis politiques, l'image de Néron jouant de la lyre pendant que Rome brûle est entrée dans la légende. La reconstruction qui suivit imposa de nouveaux règlements de construction, avec des rues plus larges et des matériaux plus résistants, changeant à jamais le visage de la Ville éternelle.", "hash": "sha256:67a0c4c728e8b7c3da78359703c7a65afea3b1a8a6f8731e0bf1d990a9d1c2ef"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L'incendie de Rome en 64 apr. J.-C....", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:29:58Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:29:42Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:ff6720c8134add9c74c3011983902ae30958819ae0c08f5b0d2ce6495c38aaec", "start": 0, "end": 924, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "incendie de Rome", "span": [2, 18], "weight": null, "norm": "incendie de rome", "embedding_ref": "emb:74553477774f54ae02e4ec9d27d3e297ff3b2757754d1df417dfbc919e85019e"}, {"expression": "64 apr. J.-C.", "span": [22, 35], "weight": null, "norm": "64 apr. j.-c.", "embedding_ref": "emb:aeda12d5a4900717c055f4d0747f377b9724d5ed2a37fea8c6533f61043a3b4b"}, {"expression": "l'Antiquité", "span": [84, 95], "weight": null, "norm": "l'antiquité", "embedding_ref": "emb:ce685079fe3af2ec09bfdf144a7c86bc314975847dbe6e5c638ea91416a8537b"}, {"expression": "l'empereur Néron", "span": [411, 427], "weight": null, "norm": "l'empereur néron", "embedding_ref": "emb:7b2e89be9259e6db0014c4fb51bcadfc541d3922bef3096bc667970f336d820d"}, {"expression": "le Grand Cirque", "span": [127, 142], "weight": null, "norm": "le grand cirque", "embedding_ref": "emb:be9382a63e12eedd0df7e602cc20945a24b89a060d8919a1175065f6e5cc05fb"}, {"expression": "le feu", "span": [144, 150], "weight": null, "norm": "le feu", "embedding_ref": "emb:ab80a82ff6439208b43a9cd405d704b52e35ac59f95f4806fd9875c2e27f7ff7"}, {"expression": "les ruelles étroites", "span": [184, 204], "weight": null, "norm": "les ruelles étroites", "embedding_ref": "emb:3dbc31653bfa4ec06a0d5c786cc4d57f2d7f41e9ddfb4e62d12ee6a65db95223"}, {"expression": "les immeubles de bois", "span": [208, 229], "weight": null, "norm": "les immeubles de bois", "embedding_ref": "emb:afb56e1e836f51e3fb21cabf1525bf8174efdb2aa7135c6238e99831e998a1b6"}, {"expression": "la Ville éternelle", "span": [905, 923], "weight": null, "norm": "la ville éternelle", "embedding_ref": "emb:e1354336fdc18d9f437cb43e10d5a9a455ee6abb5228620731aef89735ee8db3"}, {"expression": "la Domus Aurea", "span": [523, 537], "weight": null, "norm": "la domus aurea", "embedding_ref": "emb:5afbc96143cae13b835cb9282b03c6e9836307796354031d0edef25b8786bf5f"}, {"expression": "l'image de Néron", "span": [651, 667], "weight": null, "norm": "l'image de néron", "embedding_ref": "emb:41367ea9bd3d095ec3e918998dbfd6bb825c9f15f499c4e61d61fe0a5b5a4a56"}, {"expression": "la lyre", "span": [678, 685], "weight": null, "norm": "la lyre", "embedding_ref": "emb:05b325a1654a1c6bfb7c25f1506594b6423e1febb66d62d81dcb5cdad56f53d9"}, {"expression": "la légende", "span": [725, 735], "weight": null, "norm": "la légende", "embedding_ref": "emb:02cf1ea68f8902b6a5b4f10165b5fa13e117fa8fc38ec7efe69dc96ec00b9a04"}, {"expression": "de nouveaux règlements de construction", "span": [773, 811], "weight": null, "norm": "de nouveaux règlements de construction", "embedding_ref": "emb:25e862c3143b20d9ece4e3568b7564ea5d391e4f9b57f1411ecbbaa77f2f9cfb"}, {"expression": "des rues plus larges", "span": [818, 838], "weight": null, "norm": "des rues plus larges", "embedding_ref": "emb:842aa24261ba48cca881274f9fe536dc8efb88f6c4eb53c7377c18362d62efcb"}, {"expression": "des matériaux plus résistants", "span": [842, 871], "weight": null, "norm": "des matériaux plus résistants", "embedding_ref": "emb:c6c15fa25ce523918a1f0036ab7c98bd3ebeb9267681111bc22471714fa46476"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 2, "source_expression": "l'Antiquité"}}}, {"id": 7017204795762457170, "score": 0.7885814905166626, "combined_score": 0.7885814905166626, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:df0ef0095f1999b7b078e5a2ca4b618f8337aede4e074ba61af9a4352a2b2379", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:6ee35579a21ab7852a08629b73d770a8a58131404a5fa033f9e8696d470dbb07"}, "content": {"text": "Le nihilisme russe du XIXe siècle émerge comme une force intellectuelle et sociale radicale, incarnée par des figures littéraires comme Bazarov dans \"Pères et Fils\" de Tourgueniev. Ce courant rejette les autorités traditionnelles, la religion, l'art pour l'art et les conventions sociales, prônant un utilitarisme froid et une foi dans la science. Les nihilistes russes, souvent issus de la jeune intelligentsia, cherchent à détruire pour reconstruire, mais leur négation absolue débouche parfois sur un vide existentiel, exploré par Dostoïevski dans \"Les Démons\". Ce mouvement prépare le terrain pour des idéologies révolutionnaires plus structurées.", "hash": "sha256:b8757a1afb6e2d0add6a7606fa2233974c5d16b5e2dd5b1fc8bbc95872e8c62b"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "Le nihilisme russe du XIXe siècle...", "document_date": "15-03-1862", "keywords": ["#nihilisme", "#Russie", "#XIXe", "#Dostoïevski", "#Bazarov"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:41:26Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:41:17Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:cb6c40a15f3aa3a1db40f6c31fac4cde3bf573677a7b82af62433132e97d9b90", "start": 0, "end": 651, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "nihilisme russe", "span": [3, 18], "weight": null, "norm": "nihilisme russe", "embedding_ref": "emb:d68f39a0cd11497804cac4da7487222bb104251b5c0f327f3a41c77daf3cb808"}, {"expression": "XIXe siècle", "span": [22, 33], "weight": null, "norm": "xixe siècle", "embedding_ref": "emb:75c919bd2bf1ab2cf1e5a36f7aa7c578d79bbb1e7c8d7165b3d585eb17e9d4b4"}, {"expression": "figures littéraires", "span": [110, 129], "weight": null, "norm": "figures littéraires", "embedding_ref": "emb:1c2163762a13ce2155bc267986147e467afee486c2c26fa83c05998daeb350a0"}, {"expression": "Bazarov", "span": [136, 143], "weight": null, "norm": "bazarov", "embedding_ref": "emb:bb72ec010c0f9ae909d61dd79cc9fed55c3e99f80d0fcf80a581967635b60f51"}, {"expression": "Pères et Fils", "span": [150, 163], "weight": null, "norm": "pères et fils", "embedding_ref": "emb:3894d9f2bd6ed8e84f2f5e58b05e562b3de04ac1b426ade871251c1122852b51"}, {"expression": "Tourgueniev", "span": [168, 179], "weight": null, "norm": "tourgueniev", "embedding_ref": "emb:dc2d57b4a9dc5c64c4ac597a230e0f167dd3880bf4ccb093382b7b0ce22d5671"}, {"expression": "jeune intelligentsia", "span": [391, 411], "weight": null, "norm": "jeune intelligentsia", "embedding_ref": "emb:eb19335b5d1b1d47797ace745de1b7a89d994bfbd255ad16384314d9a27e2c96"}, {"expression": "Dostoïevski", "span": [534, 545], "weight": null, "norm": "dostoïevski", "embedding_ref": "emb:005706e09c559769b99967e2af1995e8cd70cfc53dc0bc5e7bfe8dc84ac69081"}, {"expression": "Les Démons", "span": [552, 562], "weight": null, "norm": "les démons", "embedding_ref": "emb:c4dc15868ef386d630a69d4b583e8b1bd1b8250b01afe0e7649347a9cd6f524c"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 2, "source_expression": "figures littéraires"}}}, {"id": 9150783051767170195, "score": 0.7714612483978271, "combined_score": 0.7714612483978271, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:d285ac498df87cefc9a3c681597989909b100dcbd7f146f9d616dc76f4133bb3", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:6bd0233029b497e462606d2edcd02ba0d8d51319a51ab31cc1b12cd2c887b746"}, "content": {"text": "La dialectique hégélienne constitue un pilier central de la philosophie de Georg Wilhelm Friedrich Hegel. Elle décrit un processus dynamique de développement où une idée initiale, la thèse, engendre sa propre contradiction, l'antithèse. Le conflit entre ces deux opposés n'est pas une impasse, mais se résout dans une synthèse supérieure, qui dépasse et conserve à la fois les éléments des moments précédents. Cette synthèse devient à son tour une nouvelle thèse, initiant un nouveau cycle. Ce mouvement, souvent résumé par la triade thèse-antithèse-synthèse, est pour Hegel la logique même du réel, s'appliquant à l'histoire, à la pensée et à l'Esprit absolu. Il ne s'agit pas d'un simple mécanisme formel, mais du déploiement nécessaire de la rationalité dans le monde.", "hash": "sha256:228d4684788d031eaa5045012d13752d3eb8df846b9e9bf7f55fc0179f53096c"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "La dialectique hégélienne : une introduction", "document_date": "15-03-2024", "keywords": ["#Hegel", "#dialectique", "#philosophie", "#thèse", "#antithèse", "#synthèse"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:30:50Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:30:38Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:0a4328aa15899f882a54f0cbd76c04d3ae0e39a5afbcf38f57f55e496038bb16", "start": 0, "end": 771, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "dialectique hégélienne", "span": [3, 25], "weight": null, "norm": "dialectique hégélienne", "embedding_ref": "emb:38e34a5342f0fee70f3c574ddbfbb572e88d53fe4d000c0491cb310581243425"}, {"expression": "philosophie de Georg Wilhelm Friedrich Hegel", "span": [60, 104], "weight": null, "norm": "philosophie de georg wilhelm friedrich hegel", "embedding_ref": "emb:7cc2c3cb4bcd89331e7ca951481f88523b8954cc9ed98544959a98c8c5fcfae5"}, {"expression": "processus dynamique de développement", "span": [121, 157], "weight": null, "norm": "processus dynamique de développement", "embedding_ref": "emb:07ee75d9216c77184ac5b8cec8c8080be2265588d01b32f7e10cbcb5de22c74a"}, {"expression": "thèse", "span": [183, 188], "weight": null, "norm": "thèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:ab527fd13cdd6cdd85551c4a1976aac0687245b63acd0c0e5d78d3f9355b41d3"}, {"expression": "antithèse", "span": [226, 235], "weight": null, "norm": "antithèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:01bcad38d5a7c890ba78682d73b42ab26c8e497419e515544d6ff06477678fc2"}, {"expression": "synthèse supérieure", "span": [318, 337], "weight": null, "norm": "synthèse supérieure", "embedding_ref": "emb:d80dff977a4f100dcca0af48a07a63880a28a4e15eafa69f9d46ad6e0d8a5d60"}, {"expression": "cycle", "span": [484, 489], "weight": null, "norm": "cycle", "embedding_ref": "emb:0502fa26959da6970c114e8bd52b86961a5a22432ce60526b994e798a95a7519"}, {"expression": "mouvement", "span": [494, 503], "weight": null, "norm": "mouvement", "embedding_ref": "emb:870bf23f917af4136b837393362c7b45b819664d51fe768f7533dc97dbbf0491"}, {"expression": "triade thèse-antithèse-synthèse", "span": [527, 558], "weight": null, "norm": "triade thèse-antithèse-synthèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:daf06bdef56ced5e9064a72de6098cc3f4dd9d37ed7774b31d72cef03053cdb1"}, {"expression": "Hegel", "span": [99, 104], "weight": null, "norm": "hegel", "embedding_ref": "emb:4b3cff3cb8638c7da59a752cc5989eab9867ff248e5bbeac3841051cf7b9771b"}, {"expression": "logique même du réel", "span": [578, 598], "weight": null, "norm": "logique même du réel", "embedding_ref": "emb:2371a7e3bd8a568de242772a62997e3b8794bdd9e3bc63aea9b43d35a09d81c8"}, {"expression": "rationalité", "span": [745, 756], "weight": null, "norm": "rationalité", "embedding_ref": "emb:99a6e697b26c1e0bae1ffae26139c31fdef3d6fb809eb4eeb616c8a58307eb7b"}, {"expression": "monde", "span": [765, 770], "weight": null, "norm": "monde", "embedding_ref": "emb:e80fc00f1300a8e6bcf64db4b2fcd54d71a60b7f95b15e3ba95cd950ed2a94f8"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 12, "source_expression": "monde"}}}, {"id": 4582868285239474243, "score": 0.7714611887931824, "combined_score": 0.7714611887931824, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:66073022ae39eac8bedc013cdf0c3b6985bf5eb31a06a3577505783032bf45c4", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://philosophie-continentale.org/dialectique/hegel-synthese"], "url": "https://philosophie-continentale.org/dialectique/hegel-synthese", "source_id": "src:7be4ec5fdf2126193051ce4fb63c17e20c498ab40ada3fff7caf4b90f3584225"}, "content": {"text": "La dialectique hégélienne constitue un mouvement ternaire fondamental : thèse, antithèse et synthèse. Ce processus ne doit pas être compris comme une simple opposition mécanique, mais comme le déploiement immanent de l'Esprit absolu. La contradiction n'est pas un échec de la pensée, mais le moteur même du réel et de son intelligibilité. Chaque moment, en niant le précédent, le conserve et l'élève à un niveau supérieur, dans une *Aufhebung* qui est à la fois suppression, conservation et dépassement. Ainsi, l'histoire de la philosophie et l'histoire du monde progressent par cette négation déterminée, où chaque synthèse devient à son tour la thèse d'un nouveau cycle dialectique.", "hash": "sha256:208a870dcf036e91dce426a0dce557ec2a2e608707981a4d2879f070bf24dab5"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "La dialectique hégélienne constitue un...", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:42:09Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:42:01Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:aa28b57e32004c5552fa1b7f455e98039d302ceec112dc4e86848b8b29096801", "start": 0, "end": 684, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "dialectique hégélienne", "span": [3, 25], "weight": null, "norm": "dialectique hégélienne", "embedding_ref": "emb:8c7161853e849abf1838362acc541edb8de6c641810bc47be4fa9b772d322a13"}, {"expression": "thèse", "span": [72, 77], "weight": null, "norm": "thèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:989df6079ce0f32bd8e28ad84687d9041c9473fe0b5f13910116da3f78e5dbb5"}, {"expression": "antithèse", "span": [79, 88], "weight": null, "norm": "antithèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:e971ecc400b5623db0d7768cd2370a1be5373f64ee71a8debb8294473fb44077"}, {"expression": "synthèse", "span": [92, 100], "weight": null, "norm": "synthèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:64d61c5035fccdfb17aa3d5fc124bc7488b0447b5dfa3ed00f79b919e6271887"}, {"expression": "Esprit absolu", "span": [219, 232], "weight": null, "norm": "esprit absolu", "embedding_ref": "emb:29db7277a9615e7e5f0d54c28ac368bd4d80721205557450976211468666941b"}, {"expression": "contradiction", "span": [237, 250], "weight": null, "norm": "contradiction", "embedding_ref": "emb:d45c1d38abd8bd22f71c931fe9eb97d35ac7d9936d819446223bcc125a178789"}, {"expression": "réel", "span": [307, 311], "weight": null, "norm": "réel", "embedding_ref": "emb:ad521e2e2a4f6b92da4b0be9823be11ea94cf9e236366fb7c93312130886a850"}, {"expression": "intelligibilité", "span": [322, 337], "weight": null, "norm": "intelligibilité", "embedding_ref": "emb:cc52d417fe60cafd392b735e976ecd584aa1c3e5ad4093d8484b1a1cbabb147e"}, {"expression": "Aufhebung", "span": [433, 442], "weight": null, "norm": "aufhebung", "embedding_ref": "emb:9b178386e8b3cbd225e612a5527faf37ca7527663141f0ff9431c23487969dd6"}, {"expression": "philosophie", "span": [528, 539], "weight": null, "norm": "philosophie", "embedding_ref": "emb:bf2adf8df5c52f1a677fafaeb677f7353230de288301b225777c6738804fe930"}, {"expression": "monde", "span": [557, 562], "weight": null, "norm": "monde", "embedding_ref": "emb:8a44c4e34a724bdaa9b05cf6695b1858aa612cffde5f5680e535fd01efff07ee"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 10, "source_expression": "monde"}}}, {"id": 5421898860283355214, "score": 0.7632306814193726, "combined_score": 0.7632306814193726, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:632f4753b8cb581d610816cfe444d7262429cdbc1872b7857e3c5cc606116c47", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://philosophie.histoire.org/dialectique-hegel"], "url": "https://philosophie.histoire.org/dialectique-hegel", "source_id": "src:2542a957dca62c561c9dba6ae01ac7c9b197ba09ebe67116d728bb52e4285010"}, "content": {"text": "La dialectique hégélienne constitue un pilier de la philosophie moderne. Elle décrit un processus dynamique où une idée initiale, la thèse, engendre sa contradiction, l'antithèse. Le conflit entre ces deux opposés se résout dans une synthèse supérieure, qui devient à son tour une nouvelle thèse. Ce mouvement, nommé Aufhebung, dépasse et conserve les moments précédents. Hegel applique cette logique à l'histoire, à l'esprit et à la réalité elle-même, voyant dans ce développement la raison immanente du monde.", "hash": "sha256:260f005ed3d0af8516c4e8a5633ecef4b29ab86b162bba5057312742bada7249"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "La dialectique hégélienne : thèse, antithèse, synthèse", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:31:32Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:31:23Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:f9f823f69b7ee72fe76b39b866fc363a41988f8b990265673fe23aaa706f3cc2", "start": 0, "end": 511, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "dialectique hégélienne", "span": [3, 25], "weight": null, "norm": "dialectique hégélienne", "embedding_ref": "emb:94736f29f33cd123c6ca3746dc9c75900555e1dccbfb4986bb21e64c4271ecc9"}, {"expression": "philosophie moderne", "span": [52, 71], "weight": null, "norm": "philosophie moderne", "embedding_ref": "emb:76e4d37bf2d3ddd7f3f873307ab722797258065d5198fdcfa0f509684c6c5c67"}, {"expression": "idée initiale", "span": [115, 128], "weight": null, "norm": "idée initiale", "embedding_ref": "emb:ff2bbe2840f06419ae169cb61bd6ba0a782ea91c0f8bd21f0a7346e5abdbbad8"}, {"expression": "thèse", "span": [133, 138], "weight": null, "norm": "thèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:621f9ebda770bce0272fe4e0e04e5747084979c081f258875bf89081d492a747"}, {"expression": "antithèse", "span": [169, 178], "weight": null, "norm": "antithèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:6a6dabaf57d9c277864e100e13378b307802825d765d3907b9479f4e46312a4c"}, {"expression": "synthèse supérieure", "span": [233, 252], "weight": null, "norm": "synthèse supérieure", "embedding_ref": "emb:3317c704a14184c8db7b4f7c8528e6d7c6ab5e899bacdb36caa4d9d6bdfe74ea"}, {"expression": "nouvelle thèse", "span": [281, 295], "weight": null, "norm": "nouvelle thèse", "embedding_ref": "emb:c3b0e1064314db46afbf5ab770bc6b90447bbf10112d106f0abc787d1e45253b"}, {"expression": "mouvement", "span": [300, 309], "weight": null, "norm": "mouvement", "embedding_ref": "emb:acf7526caee9e9825552cce90e163d1fc03d068c7ec84c53ba59e5f7a83e8d49"}, {"expression": "Aufhebung", "span": [317, 326], "weight": null, "norm": "aufhebung", "embedding_ref": "emb:a0d2a8b446f683e996d53258b7e9f3c913677e10576bbf735f4173b9f9e54d59"}, {"expression": "l'histoire", "span": [403, 413], "weight": null, "norm": "l'histoire", "embedding_ref": "emb:04fe4ff3580e6e92a2bd4ee7f428c12176ee47f77ca85d9e66ebc23aad227ead"}, {"expression": "l'esprit", "span": [417, 425], "weight": null, "norm": "l'esprit", "embedding_ref": "emb:b466c8da7d84ff56415f39adc6211e3a66d27e77a3876872bef0deadb49f4e92"}, {"expression": "la réalité", "span": [431, 441], "weight": null, "norm": "la réalité", "embedding_ref": "emb:315e2796e12a3a25476e6223360fd470cb735449673364250e7d6d5a1865a660"}, {"expression": "la raison immanente du monde", "span": [482, 510], "weight": null, "norm": "la raison immanente du monde", "embedding_ref": "emb:5715766adb111369b019263c693ef9dac296f2a49697f076445876fda52398d5"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 3, "source_expression": "thèse"}}}], "warning": null}
