2026-03-14T20:02:02	session_messenger	CHAT	SECRETARIUS	{"status": "ok", "tool": "search_text", "message": "Recherche semantique executee.", "query": "La Mésopotamie possédait-elle des ordinateurs", "summary": {"collection_name": "secretarius_semantic_graph", "query_count": 2, "hit_lists": 2, "top_k": 10, "min_score": 0.75, "keyword_query_count": 0}, "documents": [{"id": 1754547779587418120, "score": 0.9954980611801147, "combined_score": 1.0454980611801148, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:c50dffef196395e46dd8622dae37b748ac72fa807a69645b83e10339d52a245e", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:071f8f36a3934d39935dbc15dfc7f4419f1c8515d48912141ef1851e27d1fc6d"}, "content": {"text": "L'écriture est née de la nécessité de fixer la pensée et de transmettre l'information au-delà de l'oralité. Les premières traces apparaissent en Mésopotamie avec l'écriture cunéiforme, suivie des hiéroglyphes égyptiens. Chaque civilisation a développé son propre système, des idéogrammes chinois à l'alphabet phénicien, ancêtre de la plupart des écritures modernes. Cette invention a fondamentalement transformé les sociétés, permettant l'administration, la littérature et la préservation du savoir à travers les siècles.", "hash": "sha256:b02a251b296a0361b408c481354ade62379d0a92f6c62ce460845fd07d17b62d"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L'évolution des systèmes d'écriture", "document_date": "15-03-2023", "keywords": ["#écriture", "#histoire", "#civilisation"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:27Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:19Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:02f156e3eab86c2ba3e6ab70b567447119c87f9c6500280ef50f005c16c74288", "start": 0, "end": 521, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "écriture", "span": [2, 10], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture", "embedding_ref": "emb:14dbf2140003b3f9514a659dcfea18b7a8d252a0f73f1e06db724bf87aa0bbd2"}, {"expression": "Mésopotamie", "span": [145, 156], "weight": null, "norm": "mésopotamie", "embedding_ref": "emb:2161e2cb7e9e0bd12679781125917bc1873f48cbc720ba6ceed40bde80745a5d"}, {"expression": "écriture cunéiforme", "span": [164, 183], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture cunéiforme", "embedding_ref": "emb:da96b1f5f39adf551773eed24f7636dc2fa2787977e0f730db56bccb2d9a9442"}, {"expression": "hiéroglyphes égyptiens", "span": [196, 218], "weight": null, "norm": "hiéroglyphes égyptiens", "embedding_ref": "emb:c9a27a0e76526f9e12cc5929a98a2e948f391980919e316c0e6a94fb3382d574"}, {"expression": "idéogrammes chinois", "span": [276, 295], "weight": null, "norm": "idéogrammes chinois", "embedding_ref": "emb:09f8d4f312d050a8084b3973d7d99b0407344f32b3102cc19cf91b94378d5dfd"}, {"expression": "alphabet phénicien", "span": [300, 318], "weight": null, "norm": "alphabet phénicien", "embedding_ref": "emb:4b68e41be67918155cec3c7139bd1b88e3ad1f88b17deca64bd9fa9027b214d9"}, {"expression": "écritures modernes", "span": [346, 364], "weight": null, "norm": "écritures modernes", "embedding_ref": "emb:2f3c4fb0a87bb7f6009abd1ce1dd748ee78ace1cbcc0053ab86fc31195f32559"}, {"expression": "administration", "span": [439, 453], "weight": null, "norm": "administration", "embedding_ref": "emb:28f3ac334055784782b32060aa6aa3d1fcd6c8942f41fea07630f29c8eb0352e"}, {"expression": "littérature", "span": [458, 469], "weight": null, "norm": "littérature", "embedding_ref": "emb:3f74484df1a2eb2f9ac82a971c3f782cfa9a1a134042d9c9d7696ec8767b5575"}, {"expression": "préservation du savoir", "span": [476, 498], "weight": null, "norm": "préservation du savoir", "embedding_ref": "emb:d2fc6f73ab8168ff2090a2426cee06a5650fe7c28c0bb5f733f91aa165e9d7d8"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 1, "source_expression": "Mésopotamie"}}}, {"id": 7029120031433603817, "score": 0.99549800157547, "combined_score": 0.99549800157547, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:87d0e17451d26c96e994b156255d8bba2652b07aeeab937d4689dec896df58b3", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://www.histoire-ecriture.org/evolution"], "url": "https://www.histoire-ecriture.org/evolution", "source_id": "src:ea74af40c6044674cb2a2801f36442a2c58c3ac4a442f6860ea7221ac454e2f1"}, "content": {"text": "L'écriture est née il y a plus de cinq mille ans en Mésopotamie, sous la forme de pictogrammes cunéiformes sur des tablettes d'argile. Cette invention majeure a révolutionné la transmission des connaissances, permettant de fixer la langue et de développer l'administration, le commerce et la littérature. Différents systèmes ont émergé indépendamment à travers le monde, comme les hiéroglyphes égyptiens, les caractères chinois ou les glyphes mayas. Chaque système reflète la culture et les besoins de la société qui l'a créé. L'évolution vers des alphabets phonétiques, comme l'alphabet phénicien puis grec, a simplifié l'apprentissage et favorisé la diffusion de l'écrit. Aujourd'hui, l'écriture numérique poursuit cette longue histoire, transformant à nouveau nos modes de communication et de conservation de la mémoire collective.", "hash": "sha256:339efc948ebcd4b2dbb38dc831e89fd5d561c0b3f3c2e23dbbf72767a6a20e86"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L'écriture est née il y a plus de cinq...", "document_date": "15-03-2023", "keywords": ["#écriture", "#histoire", "#civilisation"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:34:05Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:33:55Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:1a8d1d1f4eae9012cd2220dbe6a3f51d114a68ddd77947ff9f3b090e94f75579", "start": 0, "end": 834, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "écriture", "span": [2, 10], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture", "embedding_ref": "emb:6e3dd1665707e650c474cde7c6c0773d817ad0eb8b34f3e4799e1261d9b296d4"}, {"expression": "Mésopotamie", "span": [52, 63], "weight": null, "norm": "mésopotamie", "embedding_ref": "emb:641d835aa88d5107e88c39c83f76d849aaaa38ea4c0124a1e41459431d266431"}, {"expression": "pictogrammes cunéiformes", "span": [82, 106], "weight": null, "norm": "pictogrammes cunéiformes", "embedding_ref": "emb:50087cd4157a0a243a06357662a58e93db32f95e859485a5471c706db3d6b0ad"}, {"expression": "tablettes d'argile", "span": [115, 133], "weight": null, "norm": "tablettes d'argile", "embedding_ref": "emb:14906245b0b6ebcec41814bc299af1e64c493c79cbbbdd299f1fc4d5267fad26"}, {"expression": "alphabet phénicien", "span": [579, 597], "weight": null, "norm": "alphabet phénicien", "embedding_ref": "emb:4e1264d17ab9773ae7745309bab7947f18e172053ed620a330b12044a4f8587c"}, {"expression": "écriture numérique", "span": [689, 707], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture numérique", "embedding_ref": "emb:9cbab327e1ea4fd831015750e360462dfe0006ba2eedeabecb57fee322efbdaf"}, {"expression": "modes de communication", "span": [767, 789], "weight": null, "norm": "modes de communication", "embedding_ref": "emb:fd69429a0e73983da8c047eeb57f8cd736ae115d6eb40ba653af303d34b752ee"}, {"expression": "conservation de la mémoire collective", "span": [796, 833], "weight": null, "norm": "conservation de la mémoire collective", "embedding_ref": "emb:f629b8ac29b6177ac7479910dd12475aeea9f9edadb1da5ae19588e9913fc8b4"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 1, "source_expression": "Mésopotamie"}}}, {"id": 8416059977206926350, "score": 0.8792274594306946, "combined_score": 0.8792274594306946, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:0b025a52eb86b28167ecd0480f4d3811f04a21f6eaa450dbb98f47b3a2b21d53", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:6e133ef014ee3aaa86044c86fa7c61e570c46f3e037a1c4eb693773be6c7a4af"}, "content": {"text": "La cybernétique, fondée par Norbert Wiener, étudie les systèmes de commande et de communication chez l'être vivant et la machine. Elle repose sur le concept de rétroaction, où l'information sur le résultat d'une action est renvoyée pour en réguler le comportement. Cette approche interdisciplinaire a influencé des domaines comme l'informatique, la biologie et les sciences sociales. Wiener voyait dans la cybernétique un moyen de comprendre et de modéliser les processus complexes, qu'ils soient naturels ou artificiels.", "hash": "sha256:f3e98d12221f60af0b4429c4a3caebf3f5c2af4e640632fe395e9a4956f50325"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "La cybernétique, fondée par Norbert...", "document_date": "15-05-1948", "keywords": ["#cybernétique", "#NorbertWiener", "#rétroaction", "#systèmes", "#communication"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:36:59Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:36:52Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:8a9ccca78ac59fb37fee827b072f87c2faca0952d8311f8195594e690aca37e0", "start": 0, "end": 521, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "Norbert Wiener", "span": [28, 42], "weight": null, "norm": "norbert wiener", "embedding_ref": "emb:c183f7ae3e493436692e47ef6d719f35a8101ea447ef2307a88771913f1c8863"}, {"expression": "cybernétique", "span": [3, 15], "weight": null, "norm": "cybernétique", "embedding_ref": "emb:86a0398de9cce0dd36df8218147835e197ba40540bc08e326aeb9593e2fefd1e"}, {"expression": "systèmes de commande", "span": [55, 75], "weight": null, "norm": "systèmes de commande", "embedding_ref": "emb:4c16fb3b17b9e0777bd0334bfda48611f40e3971222d01aaed47d989f0ba262a"}, {"expression": "être vivant", "span": [103, 114], "weight": null, "norm": "être vivant", "embedding_ref": "emb:70c8f67d7735f1e77279d38683208ba8fe122f6d1a20518d6abf678cd82b9177"}, {"expression": "machine", "span": [121, 128], "weight": null, "norm": "machine", "embedding_ref": "emb:3a4897059b8440e45ee8934577a61d2c62feca436a24f875999650689b18947a"}, {"expression": "concept de rétroaction", "span": [149, 171], "weight": null, "norm": "concept de rétroaction", "embedding_ref": "emb:251389fc75a660a6bde7efd7fcbb135e0e1c3