at d'une action est renvoyée pour en réguler le comportement. Cette approche interdisciplinaire a influencé des domaines comme l'informatique, la biologie et les sciences sociales. Wiener voyait dans la cybernétique un moyen de comprendre et de modéliser les processus complexes, qu'ils soient naturels ou artificiels.", "hash": "sha256:f3e98d12221f60af0b4429c4a3caebf3f5c2af4e640632fe395e9a4956f50325"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "La cybernétique, fondée par Norbert...", "document_date": "15-05-1948", "keywords": ["#cybernétique", "#NorbertWiener", "#rétroaction", "#systèmes", "#communication"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:36:59Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:36:52Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:8a9ccca78ac59fb37fee827b072f87c2faca0952d8311f8195594e690aca37e0", "start": 0, "end": 521, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "Norbert Wiener", "span": [28, 42], "weight": null, "norm": "norbert wiener", "embedding_ref": "emb:c183f7ae3e493436692e47ef6d719f35a8101ea447ef2307a88771913f1c8863"}, {"expression": "cybernétique", "span": [3, 15], "weight": null, "norm": "cybernétique", "embedding_ref": "emb:86a0398de9cce0dd36df8218147835e197ba40540bc08e326aeb9593e2fefd1e"}, {"expression": "systèmes de commande", "span": [55, 75], "weight": null, "norm": "systèmes de commande", "embedding_ref": "emb:4c16fb3b17b9e0777bd0334bfda48611f40e3971222d01aaed47d989f0ba262a"}, {"expression": "être vivant", "span": [103, 114], "weight": null, "norm": "être vivant", "embedding_ref": "emb:70c8f67d7735f1e77279d38683208ba8fe122f6d1a20518d6abf678cd82b9177"}, {"expression": "machine", "span": [121, 128], "weight": null, "norm": "machine", "embedding_ref": "emb:3a4897059b8440e45ee8934577a61d2c62feca436a24f875999650689b18947a"}, {"expression": "concept de rétroaction", "span": [149, 171], "weight": null, "norm": "concept de rétroaction", "embedding_ref": "emb:251389fc75a660a6bde7efd7fcbb135e0e1c30f5ec8d32beb56055e40d8406bb"}, {"expression": "informat