}, {"id": 1754547779587418120, "score": 1.0000001192092896, "combined_score": 1.0000001192092896, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:c50dffef196395e46dd8622dae37b748ac72fa807a69645b83e10339d52a245e", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:071f8f36a3934d39935dbc15dfc7f4419f1c8515d48912141ef1851e27d1fc6d"}, "content": {"text": "L'écriture est née de la nécessité de fixer la pensée et de transmettre l'information au-delà de l'oralité. Les premières traces apparaissent en Mésopotamie avec l'écriture cunéiforme, suivie des hiéroglyphes égyptiens. Chaque civilisation a développé son propre système, des idéogrammes chinois à l'alphabet phénicien, ancêtre de la plupart des écritures modernes. Cette invention a fondamentalement transformé les sociétés, permettant l'administration, la littérature et la préservation du savoir à travers les siècles.", "hash": "sha256:b02a251b296a0361b408c481354ade62379d0a92f6c62ce460845fd07d17b62d"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L'évolution des systèmes d'écriture", "document_date": "15-03-2023", "keywords": ["#écriture", "#histoire", "#civilisation"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:27Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:43:19Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:02f156e3eab86c2ba3e6ab70b567447119c87f9c6500280ef50f005c16c74288", "start": 0, "end": 521, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "écriture", "span": [2, 10], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture", "embedding_ref": "emb:14dbf2140003b3f9514a659dcfea18b7a8d252a0f73f1e06db724bf87aa0bbd2"}, {"expression": "Mésopotamie", "span": [145, 156], "weight": null, "norm": "mésopotamie", "embedding_ref": "emb:2161e2cb7e9e0bd12679781125917bc1873f48cbc720ba6ceed40bde80745a5d"}, {"expression": "écriture cunéiforme", "span": [164, 183], "weight": null, "norm": "écriture cunéiforme", "embedding_ref": "emb:da96b1f5f39adf551773eed24f7636dc2fa2787977e0f730db56bccb2d9a9442"}, {"expression": "hiéroglyphes égyptiens", "span": [196, 218], "weight": null, "norm": "hiéroglyphes égyptiens", "embedding_ref": "emb:c9a27a0e76526f9e12cc5929a98a2e948f391980919e316c0e6a94fb3382d574"}, {"expression": "idéogrammes chinois", "span": [276, 295], "weight": null, "norm": "idéogrammes chinois", "embedding_ref": "emb:09f8d4f312d050a8084b3973d7d99b0407344f32b3102cc19cf91b94378d5dfd"}, {"expression": "alphabet phénicien", "span": [300, 318], "weight": null, "norm": "alphabet phénicien", "embedding_ref": "emb:4b68e41be67918155cec3c7139bd1b88e3ad1f88b17deca64bd9fa9027b214d9"}, {"expression": "écritures modernes", "span": [346, 364], "weight": null, "norm": "écritures modernes", "embedding_ref": "emb:2f3c4fb0a87bb7f6009abd1ce1dd748ee78ace1cbcc0053ab86fc31195f32559"}, {"expression": "administration", "span": [439, 453], "weight": null, "norm": "administration", "embedding_ref": "emb:28f3ac334055784782b32060aa6aa3d1fcd6c8942f41fea07630f29c8eb0352e"}, {"expression": "littérature", "span": [458, 469], "weight": null, "norm": "littérature", "embedding_ref": "emb:3f74484df1a2eb2f9ac82a971c3f782cfa9a1a134042d9c9d7696ec8767b5575"}, {"expression": "préservation du savoir", "span": [476, 498], "weight": null, "norm": "préservation du savoir", "embedding_ref": "emb:d2fc6f73ab8168ff2090a2426cee06a5650fe7c28c0bb5f733f91aa165e9d7d8"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 1, "source_expression": "Mésopotamie"}}}, {"id": 5811986041007577441, "score": 0.9084038734436035, "combined_score": 0.9084038734436035, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:8bb8ccfdede8e53113b95ccd93f611406aea0111e7309a03cf320503c0ec6a5d", "type": "url", "source": {"urls": ["https://archives-ecriture.org/tablettes-mesopotamie"], "url": "https://archives-ecriture.org/tablettes-mesopotamie", "source_id": "src:56973aff0c69bec46e38aa19e77004f702ace5e57018a0390e1a15851201535a"}, "content": {"text": "Les premières traces d'écriture remontent à la Mésopotamie antique, vers 3300 avant notre ère. Il s'agissait de pictogrammes tracés sur des tablettes d'argile humide à l'aide d'un calame. Ce système, appelé cunéiforme, a évolué vers une écriture plus abstraite, représentant des sons et des concepts. Parallèlement, en Égypte, se développaient les hiéroglyphes, un système complexe mêlant logogrammes et signes phonétiques. L'invention de l'alphabet phénicien, vers 1200 av. J.-C., marqua une révolution en permettant de noter tous les sons d'une langue avec une trentaine de signes seulement. Cet alphabet fut adapté par les Grecs, qui y ajoutèrent les voyelles, puis transmis aux Romains. L'écriture a ainsi été le vecteur essentiel de la préservation et de la diffusion des connaissances à travers les âges.", "hash": "sha256:f98f149ecc7c00a6d88d3ece92a40f309a375c2327c7ac8308043fb3e9c6392c"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "L'évolution des systèmes graphiques", "document_date": "15-03-2023", "keywords": [], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:36:42Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:36:33Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:ba8274f214b097d147bb20af0ed3238c95592184ded5467aa4b2c8e6ccc4b557", "start": 0, "end": 810, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "pictogrammes", "span": [112, 124], "weight": null, "norm": "pictogrammes", "embedding_ref": "emb:f655ac744bcdc8dec2290fe21d2001d3278ceacf8f73db88345dde3d513a283c"}, {"expression": "tablettes d'argile humide", "span": [140, 165], "weight": null, "norm": "tablettes d'argile humide", "embedding_ref": "emb:49134305aa2a188cf4a998bb57b6eadda0dabae26a442e2c00a2a842b4c42fbb"}, {"expression": "hiéroglyphes", "span": [348, 360], "weight": null, "norm": "hiéroglyphes", "embedding_ref": "emb:d0b46c9cf1e2d7c8815c8c2a085ad7fa498b111e79807340df5b16e85ec44427"}, {"expression": "alphabet phénicien", "span": [441, 459], "weight": null, "norm": "alphabet phénicien", "embedding_ref": "emb:b45f39dfa68b40b02341aba6aa5baece4a58a614c304de8cba3f06b6ee9464fc"}, {"expression": "Grecs", "span": [626, 631], "weight": null, "norm": "grecs", "embedding_ref": "emb:1de315767e951f492ed826bcf0d28b55543a4cf8db045250dc9ddcb16a3e8612"}, {"expression": "Romains", "span": [682, 689], "weight": null, "norm": "romains", "embedding_ref": "emb:d09b0b90c8f76eab6c2dc442d4320368466501aed1ee10bb18d61145e1d10b93"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 3, "source_expression": "alphabet phénicien"}}}, {"id": 4036472102459064604, "score": 0.7629367113113403, "combined_score": 0.7629367113113403, "keyword_matches": [], "document": {"schema": "secretarius.document.v0.1", "doc_id": "doc:56a7cbe1c5d363310852ec6ad89271080f3f09b5cc0efb17da1b2f0ab865655f", "type": "note", "source": {"urls": [], "source_id": "src:5a7d59723d1cf53b05cc19e766216e75f24a148326b4cffc688cf8e3396cd248"}, "content": {"text": "Les utopies technologiques ont toujours fasciné l'humanité. Elles proposent un avenir où la technologie résout tous les problèmes, élimine la souffrance et crée une société parfaite. Des cités idéales aux intelligences artificielles bienveillantes, ces visions mêlent innovation et espoir. Pourtant, elles soulèvent aussi des questions éthiques et pratiques. La promesse d'un monde meilleur grâce aux machines coexiste avec le risque de dépendance, de surveillance et d'inégalités. Ces récits, qu'ils soient littéraires ou philosophiques, nous invitent à réfléchir à la direction que prend notre progrès. Ils nous rappellent que chaque avancée porte en elle un choix de société. L'utopie n'est peut-être pas un lieu, mais un chemin à construire, avec prudence et humanité.", "hash": "sha256:1ba3769f2360e4e4d8b654264a2b253e0ba10f916c88ebf52a75061dbb098760"}, "user_fields": {"type_note": "fugace", "title": "Les utopies technologiques : entre rêve et réalité", "keywords": ["#technologie", "#utopie", "#avenir"], "updated_at": "2026-03-14T16:33:21Z", "created_at": "2026-03-14T16:33:06Z"}, "derived": {"chunks": [{"chunk_id": "chunk:54023f33be2b6838af23fa32286108dabd14f05631641b628f60e3cb34d0f3c9", "start": 0, "end": 772, "text_ref": null}], "expressions": [{"expression": "utopies technologiques", "span": [4, 26], "weight": null, "norm": "utopies technologiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:99d9f09824104f67a3d0ca15d857cf30f14b27b579d14510ad8e78c0cb8616b7"}, {"expression": "avenir", "span": [79, 85], "weight": null, "norm": "avenir", "embedding_ref": "emb:8eaa565f677e430f4f940c5c8320bf22257c613583b40809a30116fb4a07c2c4"}, {"expression": "technologie", "span": [92, 103], "weight": null, "norm": "technologie", "embedding_ref": "emb:4f1478c87f8c6efcfc10fbefa32799f1447e32345bb7754e5c887f604d72fcd1"}, {"expression": "problèmes", "span": [120, 129], "weight": null, "norm": "problèmes", "embedding_ref": "emb:023de8b311a45c3ff23a419561d461d8dcc082bd1904befca37e3dc7c12b526d"}, {"expression": "société parfaite", "span": [165, 181], "weight": null, "norm": "société parfaite", "embedding_ref": "emb:a1c589e840a1e00fd02f548bfbc8be091b7650580f2babd8141c084ad919900f"}, {"expression": "cités idéales", "span": [187, 200], "weight": null, "norm": "cités idéales", "embedding_ref": "emb:ca15e3ab149bccd63e0d0c25ce5b0ad9eb1c2cf40302a27c94767fd6c95a94fb"}, {"expression": "intelligences artificielles", "span": [205, 232], "weight": null, "norm": "intelligences artificielles", "embedding_ref": "emb:fe313a7943b1bd168b532173e691a8c7a2f460917654f9efdfe6435a39022993"}, {"expression": "questions éthiques", "span": [326, 344], "weight": null, "norm": "questions éthiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:793c3d2b026f0bc83c9878bb1a869cc141ee963d3f17810d6ea7d2aecac91461"}, {"expression": "promesse d'un monde meilleur", "span": [362, 390], "weight": null, "norm": "promesse d'un monde meilleur", "embedding_ref": "emb:6a04c12087c7513e611a4ed1a452ff42b5f877ded4935142f83aeeb2a2c5236f"}, {"expression": "machines", "span": [401, 409], "weight": null, "norm": "machines", "embedding_ref": "emb:9909c6ffff1d613ef1c841d69102a0e9ee718ff275ce99e51f4b8d845583747f"}, {"expression": "risque de dépendance", "span": [427, 447], "weight": null, "norm": "risque de dépendance", "embedding_ref": "emb:66ae4393ecd9c04ba78e0646398e3342cd1fb80d55cf7fb96e559fff56cf4c5f"}, {"expression": "surveillance", "span": [452, 464], "weight": null, "norm": "surveillance", "embedding_ref": "emb:5745bfdc728dc097190088dfe16cb35bbc31dfd8e68604002ae8525fe11be531"}, {"expression": "inégalités", "span": [470, 480], "weight": null, "norm": "inégalités", "embedding_ref": "emb:cb76cebf840ffe3ece1353745c0ecc500c7fab15c91e677021016ea09afd83bb"}, {"expression": "récits", "span": [486, 492], "weight": null, "norm": "récits", "embedding_ref": "emb:ae269a27e453ff0ef637fdfa168d4b4f44c0e1b4fc09f20df30c573e44d1cefa"}, {"expression": "littéraires", "span": [508, 519], "weight": null, "norm": "littéraires", "embedding_ref": "emb:87cb6415d2cf0fe4351d46613fce318327d4587934d3a703d69dd022320922f4"}, {"expression": "philosophiques", "span": [523, 537], "weight": null, "norm": "philosophiques", "embedding_ref": "emb:b6c02742ba93898c10b3b4c86356f5e5ad65082ff0edd81adda20e7b8c500235"}, {"expression": "direction", "span": [570, 579], "weight": null, "norm": "direction", "embedding_ref": "emb:76d7eceb53c825e7a5d8ff773e08480fe19a64414c4770cbc4df5772fb8e76eb"}, {"expression": "progrès", "span": [596, 603], "weight": null, "norm": "progrès", "embedding_ref": "emb:783460db732f460d48e5dda2dcf34f79f26183cd65266c8e7a9210cf1464bf8f"}, {"expression": "choix de société", "span": [661, 677], "weight": null, "norm": "choix de société", "embedding_ref": "emb:2a4f5bbc5a86a7e582f2e527501576467dd146dc25911f10660e41ed5fd47bca"}, {"expression": "utopie", "span": [4, 10], "weight": null, "norm": "utopie", "embedding_ref": "emb:9c341dea9ee3402b7106a52d9ba510a91b46864ee61df651f5fd0d456239ddce"}, {"expression": "lieu", "span": [711, 715], "weight": null, "norm": "lieu", "embedding_ref": "emb:0b5a287ccbd288a8c52f745b0437081ba1b8e47335c08e79b8c57ac3f0074a01"}, {"expression": "chemin à construire", "span": [725, 744], "weight": null, "norm": "chemin à construire", "embedding_ref": "emb:32dd98310484c3527086a0870b21b3c5509f385e43e5415987b250d713ddaeca"}, {"expression": "prudence", "span": [751, 759], "weight": null, "norm": "prudence", "embedding_ref": "emb:d2e599e3ea66eb0a9ddb77feab08713db2690b1830ac2b8dd219efa30d1a0650"}, {"expression": "humanité", "span": [50, 58], "weight": null, "norm": "humanité", "embedding_ref": "emb:36296978d74047de7aaf159485d9d391f7b281fa9e52e7a6d93af1cab3685916"}]}, "indexing": {"pipeline_version": "v0.1", "state": "done", "errors": [], "source": "document_pipeline:index_text", "source_expression_idx": 14, "source_expression": "littéraires"}}}], "warning": null}
